            <text for="L21">The screaming</text>
            <text for="L22">The left arm I’ve caught with was sweet</text>
            <text for="L23">The right arm I’ve swung with was sweet</text>
            <text for="L24">It was sweet</text>
            <text for="L25">It was sweet</text>
            <text for="L26">Even if my mouth with a smile gets torn</text>
            <text for="L27">That’s just fun, so fun</text>
