            <text for="L163">Sweet</text>
            <text for="L164">Red</text>
            <text for="L165">Red</text>
            <text for="L166">Red</text>
            <text for="L167">Red</text>
            <text for="L168">Red</text>
            <text for="L169">You... So sweet!</text>
            <text for="L170">Sweet</text>
            <text for="L171">Red</text>
            <text for="L172">Red</text>
            <text for="L173">I’ll kill you!</text>
            <text for="L174">Your life is torn apart, you spit up something red and silver and they spray away <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(I want to stay like this, in my beautiful world...)</span></text>
            <text for="L175">I scatter the flower of your life, blooming in rich colors, and turn you into my food <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(The memories dance, let me make you mine...)</span></text>
            <text for="L176">If your life is you, then I’ll eat you up into flesh and blood <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(I’m sorry, but this is a final act of love...)</span></text>
            <text for="L177">I’ll offer up your limbs as sacrifice- Become the corpse at my feet <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Be by my side forever, I want to live with you...)</span></text>
          </translation>
